---
title: Crispy BBQ Cauliflower Naan Wraps with Pickle Slaw & Potato Chips
description: What’s not to love about vegetarian naan wraps packed with crispy fried cauliflower and a ton of backyard BBQ flavor? Along with the BBQ-spiced cauliflower, you’ll stuff these wraps with a tangy pickle slaw that brings a fresh crunch to each bite. Complete the meal with a drizzle of creamy BBQ sauce and a side of potato chips.
